WindwardRestApi.Model

Class DataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • WindwardRestApi.Model.DataSource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsonDataSource, ODataDataSource, SalesforceDataSource, SalesforceOAuthDataSource, SqlDataSource, Xml_10DataSource, Xml_20DataSource

    public abstract class DataSource
extends java.lang.Object
    A datasource to apply to a template. This can include datasets built from this datasource. Used as part of a document generation request.
